	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Blowing is not recommended. To clean Game Pak edge connectors, use a cotton swab and rubbing alcohol.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
