		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">. A few people have said slightly bending each of the 72 pins fixes it, I haven't tried that though.</div>
<br />That is definitely a great thing to do. Just bend all pins on the top part (only 36 pins), because the bottom ones aren't acessible with some random tool, and the connector will grip more games, fixing most problems.

		

